<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="KR5e0001-en-17288bed" type="transl"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>Translation of 太平經 into (English)</title><editor role="translator"/></titleStmt><publicationStmt><p>published electronically as part of the TLS project at https://hxwd.org</p><availability status="1">This work is in the public domain</availability></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><p>Created by members of the TLS project</p><p>Translation of <bibl corresp="#KR5e0001"><title xml:lang="och">太平經</title></bibl> into <lang xml:lang="en">English</lang>.</p></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><creation resp="#barbara.hendrischke">Initially created: <date>2020-05-05T20:31:11.466+09:00</date> by barbara.hendrischke</creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div><head>Translated parts</head><p xml:id="KR5e0001-start"><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.901" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2020-11-28T16:24:16.303+09:00">plant and do not reach its purpose</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1298" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-28T19:41:55.942+09:00">Considering Heaven and earth, yin yang and the ten thousand things</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1299" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-28T19:43:07.663+09:00">Above and below is mutually governing in mutual love xx</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1300" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-04-28T11:21:53.158+09:00">through which there is success and names are established.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1301" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-04-28T13:20:20.053+09:00">As it brings the mind to govern a whole family,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1302" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-04-28T15:28:06.326+09:00">so it brings people to no longer hate each other,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1303" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-04-28T15:28:28.096+09:00">and they are always happy and with a united striving.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1304" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-04-28T15:31:37.576+09:00">Cause the Qi of the great peace to appear</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1305" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-04-30T10:27:17.047+09:00">and great peace to blossom</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1306" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-04-30T10:32:45.328+09:00">The six extremeties come together in one string</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1307" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-04-30T10:36:37.178+09:00">the eight directions follow the same strategy.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1308" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-04-30T10:39:18.822+09:00">All rulers act according to the wishes of the people</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1309" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-04-30T10:41:49.608+09:00">how can this not all resound with happiness.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1310" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-04-30T10:42:29.807+09:00">The original qi of heaven and earth</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1311" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-04-30T10:43:22.833+09:00">combined with the roles of yin and yang,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1312" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-28T19:52:39.861+09:00">silences and erases the wicked,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1313" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-04-30T11:25:16.191+09:00">causes even the disobient to follow all rules,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1314" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-04-30T11:26:12.799+09:00">brighten the great sacred of the supreme way</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1315" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-04-30T11:27:42.859+09:00">and let the gods of heaven and the spirits of earth love and penetrate each other.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1316" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-04-30T11:32:32.617+09:00">I am travelling up to where Huangdi is laying out the way and the virtue</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1317" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-04-30T11:35:54.551+09:00">and down to the mountains and rivers where the signs and patterns are recognized,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1318" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-04-30T11:37:50.15+09:00">and to the middle, where the ruler is setting up the law,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1319" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-04-30T11:40:08.441+09:00">and the saints are inspired by it to their well intentions.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1320" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-03T15:28:42.263+09:00">Therefore, in order to save Heaven and Earth from the guilt of great disasters</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1321" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-03T15:30:21.573+09:00">and to relieve the Diwang from great distress,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1322" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-03T15:30:42.046+09:00">to let people love each other</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1323" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-03T15:30:58.181+09:00">and the myriad things all gain there place,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1324" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-03T16:04:34.31+09:00">the regularities of the heavenly law make themselves unhidden.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1325" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-03T16:05:02.411+09:00">For this reason, the holy Diwang of old</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1326" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-03T16:05:18.987+09:00">takes the minister seriously,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1327" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-03T16:06:40.492+09:00">loves the secluded scholar</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1328" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-03T16:06:47.791+09:00">serves the people</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1329" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-03T16:06:54.047+09:00">and does no harm.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1330" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-03T16:07:31.001+09:00">The minister on the other hand, will serve loyal and not deceive his lord,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1331" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-03T16:07:57.966+09:00">and therefore implement the acts of the gods,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1332" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-03T16:08:54.25+09:00">and as the wise father will always think about the safety of his child,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1333" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-03T16:09:24.353+09:00">the child will always think of peace and joy of the father,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1334" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-03T16:10:39.44+09:00">both join forces in the same heart,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1335" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-03T16:10:14.881+09:00">and the family can not be not created,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1336" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-03T16:10:31.89+09:00">If the two forces are not joint in the same heart,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1337" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-03T16:11:09.066+09:00">the way of the family will be in disarray.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1338" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T09:41:17.836+09:00">They lose their profession,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1339" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T09:41:30.137+09:00">arrive at extreme poverty</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1340" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T09:44:21.517+09:00">and therefore are reduced to fighting, divide and go separate ways</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1341" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T09:50:55.037+09:00">and proceed to inflict harm on each other.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1342" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T10:16:44.328+09:00">The father and son give birth to and cause the vigor arise,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1343" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T10:17:08.016+09:00">the limbs are assembled and accordingly attached,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1344" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T10:19:36.643+09:00">how can now under heaven men of different clans assemble and treat each other as lord, leader or father?</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1345" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T10:20:48.352+09:00">Therefore, because the saints of old saw a little and immediately new it,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1346" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T10:25:15.099+09:00">and they prioritize caution of it.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1347" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T10:25:23.809+09:00">Now as to the Leader,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1348" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T10:25:27.514+09:00">he is yang.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1349" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T10:25:42.924+09:00">He loves his disciples,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1350" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T10:26:01.149+09:00">leads and teaches them the good path.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1351" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T10:27:03.941+09:00">Causes them to know how to revere heaven and love earth,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1352" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T10:27:30.055+09:00">Respect the above and serve that is lowly,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1353" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T10:27:59.463+09:00">The disciples for their part respect their teacher</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1354" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T10:28:58.841+09:00">make every effort to serve him faithfully and not conspire against him.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1355" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T10:29:16.872+09:00">when both join forces in the same spirit,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1356" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T10:32:24.988+09:00">they paint [revitalize] the eternal old laws,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1357" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T10:32:40.416+09:00">put the sayings of the saints into practice,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1358" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T10:33:27.114+09:00">light up the world that has been divided into parts,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1359" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T10:33:48.181+09:00">and let the myriad things all gain their place.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1360" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T10:34:43.176+09:00">Without halt they accumulate virtue,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1361" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T10:35:46.056+09:00">and thus become an excellent servant to the Diwang,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1362" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T10:37:17.427+09:00">together with him, their stratagams combine and bring about the Great Peace according to common patterns.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1363" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T10:37:43.68+09:00">If they don't work together with common plans,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1364" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T10:39:03.226+09:00">they can not mutually transmit the keypoints of the Way,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1368" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-05-04T11:41:15.886+09:00">disarrange the words of the saints</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1376" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-06-26T15:21:10.685+09:00">From the time of birth, man has yin and yang</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1377" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-06-26T15:22:10.255+09:00">moving and resting, anger and joy, all has its time.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1378" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-06-26T15:22:50.252+09:00">At this time, the interchange of male and female does not yet occur.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1379" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-06-26T15:23:42.502+09:00">This is the result of being born under the main governance of yin and yang.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1395" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-06-26T15:26:04.423+09:00">with 25 years</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1397" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-06-26T15:36:53.464+09:00">with 30 years in the zenith of power</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1401" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-06-26T15:50:09.837+09:00">can keep going for 30 years until the sexual drive diminishes</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1391" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-06-26T15:34:16.108+09:00">with 20 years</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1392" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-06-26T15:35:34.723+09:00">the age</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1398" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-06-26T15:38:10.348+09:00">therefore the desire to implement the natural drive</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1404" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-06-26T15:42:03.62+09:00">among the  living beings under the heaven</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1405" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-06-26T15:42:33.539+09:00">only man can follow the way,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1406" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-06-26T15:42:46.736+09:00">the others can not.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1402" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-06-26T15:51:35.028+09:00">becomes old and feeble</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1403" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-06-26T15:52:59.465+09:00">and stops the proceedings of the inner chamber.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1383" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-06-26T16:00:33.218+09:00">The way of harmony after all.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1407" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-06-26T16:17:06.527+09:00">therefore, heaven and earth</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1419" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-06-26T16:37:22.518+09:00">These 2000 things,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1420" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-06-26T16:37:32.294+09:00">are precious and good things.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1421" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-06-26T16:40:36.041+09:00">These 2000 things,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1422" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-06-26T16:40:49.718+09:00">they have all their own spirit</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1423" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-06-26T16:41:03.885+09:00">and their own will,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1425" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-06-26T16:45:59.988+09:00">and thus reach mutual communion.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1424" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-06-26T16:42:38.75+09:00">and all living beings continue on the great way,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.1426" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2021-07-01T14:12:26.058+09:00"/></p></div></body></text></TEI>